Description: NetworkManager plugin for MS SSO OpenConnect (GNOME VPN UI)
 A NetworkManager VPN plugin that integrates Microsoft SSO authentication
 (via Playwright) with OpenConnect, allowing configuration and connection
 from GNOME's native VPN settings UI.
